column1: Sprint 49
Insight
Sprint Burndown - Burndown rate expected for the current sprint and how far from it the current sprint is.
Tickets Without Commits - Tickets waiting for a commit for longer than usual.
Delayed Pull Requests - Pull Requests take longer than expected in a particular stage.
Delayed Tickets - Tickets taking longer than expected in a particular status.
More Repositories Changed - More repos changed than usual on a ticket.
More Files Changed - More changed files than usual on a ticket.
Increased Developers - More developers are working on a ticket than usual.
Carryovers - Number of tickets being carried over from a previous sprint.
Distractions - Tickets being worked on outside of the sprint or epic.
Added Work - Work added after the sprint started.
